    - target: {fileID: 8045659150639517358, guid: fbcc40e91526859428bab09db558e208, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_value.<Text>k__BackingField
      value: '[nostalgic] There was a time I journeyed into the dark forest, seeking
        a legendary relic. [thoughtful] The path was treacherous, filled with unseen
        dangers and mythical beasts. [alert] I relied on my wits and bravery to survive,
        outsmarting the cunning traps set by ancient guardians. [proud] Finding that
        relic was a triumph that solidified my reputation among my peers.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
